data.description: Welcome to 636 Linden Lane, a beautiful custom home in Mustang, Oklahoma. This residence combines contemporary sophistication with the warmth of a family-friendly neighborhood, offering an ideal space for comfortable living and entertaining. The interiors boast open, spacious living areas that are ideal for both family relaxation and hosting guests. Large windows bathe the rooms in natural light, creating an inviting ambiance. The kitchen offers ample cabinet space, and a functional layout perfect for culinary adventures and social gatherings. The oversized pantry off of the laundry room provides additional storage. The property offers three generously sized bedrooms, each designed for comfort and style. The master suite with brand new carpet is a tranquil retreat with a luxurious en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. Linden Lane is part of a welcoming and safe community, offering a great environment for families and individuals alike. Updates include new fence 2021, new water heater 2020, new laminate flooring, custom kitchen cabinets, and new garage door opener 2021. Roof was replaced in 2018. This home is ideally situated, offering easy access to schools, parks, shopping centers, and major roadways, ensuring a convenient lifestyle. Schedule a visit today! Don't miss your chance to make Linden Lane your new home in​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ Mustang!
